        "text_tU4gQk": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In an effort to meet Wave's sustainability pledge, all of our products are 'Designed For Repair'. The user can resolve most issues with some basic troubleshooting or spare parts provided. We ask you to work with our customer support team via live chat or email for any questions you have and follow the troubleshooting guides below for common problems with rigid eco foam spas:</p>",
            "text_font": "body",
            "text_size": "subtext-md",
            "text_max_size": 32,
            "secondary_color": false,
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
